context: &quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lolcat&quot;
},
...
]
</code></pre>
<h5><a id="Usage_36"></a>Usage</h5>
<pre><code>https://fntgnn-fcc-image-search.herokuapp.com/imagesearch/cats
https://fntgnn-fcc-image-search.herokuapp.com/imagesearch/cats?offset=2
</code></pre>
<p>Or:</p>
<pre><code>https://fntgnn-fcc-image-search.herokuapp.com/latest
</code></pre>
